Output assets/demo.gif

Require echo

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 920
Set Height 540
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Hide
Type "export PATH=/opt/homebrew/bin:$PATH && clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "bash /tmp/advisor_demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 17s
